# Autoceny Landing Page — Definitive Redesign Guide
## Version 2.0 — Corrected Font & Color

---

## 1. Design Direction

Qapital's landing page works because of three things: a geometric sans-serif headline font at light weight, a cool mint accent on dark teal, and enormous whitespace. Everything else supports these three pillars. This document provides the exact specifications to replicate this quality for Autoceny.

The aesthetic target is **Scandinavian functionalism** — clean, geometric, precise, calm. Think IKEA packaging, Stockholm metro signage, Volvo dashboards. Not fashion. Not editorial. Not decorative. Functional beauty through simplicity.

