## 2. Typography

### Font Stack

```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

:root {
  --font-display: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
  --font-body: 'DM Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
}
```

**Josefin Sans** is the headline font — a geometric sans-serif with Scandinavian roots, inspired by 1920s-30s functionalism. It is the closest free alternative to Funkis (the paid font Qapital uses). Both share the same design DNA: clean circular geometry, even stroke weight, calm architectural precision.

**DM Sans** is the body font — neutral, geometric, excellent readability at small sizes. It pairs naturally with Josefin Sans because both are geometric but DM Sans has a higher x-height optimized for body text.

### Type Scale — Landing Page

| Token | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height | Letter Spacing | Usage |
|-------|------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|-------|
| `hero-title` | Josefin Sans | clamp(48px, 5.5vw, 72px) | 300 | 1.08 | -0.01em | Hero headline only |
| `section-title` | Josefin Sans | clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 48px) | 400 | 1.12 | -0.005em | Feature section headings |
| `overline` | DM Sans | 12px | 600 | 1.4 | 0.1em | Section labels, uppercased |
| `body-large` | DM Sans | 17px | 400 | 1.7 | 0 | Hero subtitle, section descriptions |
| `body` | DM Sans | 16px | 400 | 1.65 | 0 | General body text |
| `body-small` | DM Sans | 14px | 400 | 1.6 | 0 | Card descriptions, metadata |
| `caption` | DM Sans | 13px | 400 | 1.5 | 0.01em | Timestamps, footnotes |
| `btn-text` | DM Sans | 15px | 600 | 1 | 0.005em | Button labels |
| `nav-link` | DM Sans | 14px | 500 | 1 | 0.005em | Navigation items |
| `trust-value` | DM Sans | 22px | 700 | 1.2 | -0.01em | Trust bar numbers |
| `trust-label` | DM Sans | 12px | 500 | 1.4 | 0.08em | Trust bar descriptions, uppercased |
| `price` | DM Sans | 40px | 700 | 1.1 | -0.02em | Pricing numbers |

### Critical Typography Rules

**Hero headline must be weight 300 (Light).** This is non-negotiable. The entire Qapital aesthetic depends on thin, geometric letterforms at large sizes. Weight 400 is acceptable for section titles. Weight 500+ is only for body text emphasis. Never use 600-700 on any headline.

**Body text never uses Josefin Sans.** Josefin Sans has a low x-height that makes it harder to read at small sizes. DM Sans handles all text below 24px.

**No italic anywhere on the landing page.** Italics break the geometric, architectural feel.

**Uppercase only for overline labels** ("DLA KIEROWCÓW", "PORÓWNAJ I WYBIERZ") and trust bar descriptions. Everything else — headings, buttons, body — is sentence case.

**Maximum line length for body text: 520px** (~55-60 characters). Constrain all descriptive paragraphs with max-width.

