### Atmosphere

Add a very subtle radial gradient glow behind the visual area:
```css
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -20%;
  right: -10%;
  width: 70%;
  height: 140%;
  background: radial-gradient(
    ellipse at center,
    rgba(110, 207, 171, 0.06) 0%,
    transparent 70%
  );
}
