## 14. Scroll Animations

All content elements use scroll-triggered reveal:

```css
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
              transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}

.reveal.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
```

Stagger within sections: overline at 0ms, headline at 100ms, description at 200ms, CTA at 300ms, visual at 150ms.

Use IntersectionObserver with threshold 0.15 and rootMargin "0px 0px -40px 0px".

